data.description: From the inviting courtyard at the front door, to the amazing workshop area out back, you'll find many reasons to love this 4BD/3BA Northwest Roswell home! Set on a huge corner lot, the two master ensuites on the lower level are a rare find, and the two upstairs bedrooms share a Jack and Jill bath. Slip away to the balcony and make it your new morning coffee spot!  The backyard is a blank slate and ready for a play area, your pets, or patio furniture. An existing dog run stays. The huge concrete pad is an ideal spot for extra vehicles and/or an RV! Two small workshops with separate entries. One has a sink and AC unit; both are ready for those late-night project impulses!
